# ChurchCRM Complete Data Flow Diagrams
## Business Process Flows

---

## 1. Person Lifecycle

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph Registration["Person Registration"]
        P1["New Person<br/>Entered in person_per"]
        P2["Assign Classification<br/>per_cls_ID -> list_lst"]
        P3["Assign Family<br/>per_fam_ID -> family_fam"]
    end
    
    subgraph GroupInvolvement["Group Involvement"]
        P4["Join Groups<br/>person2group2role_p2g2r"]
        P5["Assign Group Role"]
        P6["Group Properties<br/>groupprop_master"]
    end
    
    subgraph Volunteer["Volunteer Service"]
        V1["Assign Volunteer Opportunity<br/>person2volunteeropp_p2vo"]
        V2["Track Volunteer Hours"]
    end
    
    subgraph Activities["Activities & Events"]
        A1["Event Registration<br/>event_attend"]
        A2["Check-in/Check-out"]
        A3["Event Counts<br/>eventcounts_evtcnt"]
    end
    
    P1 --> P2 --> P3 --> P4 --> P5 --> P6
    P4 --> V1 --> V2
    P4 --> A1 --> A2 --> A3
```

---

## 2. Financial Full Chain

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph Pledge["Pledge Commitment"]
        F1["Define Donation Fund<br/>donationfund_fun"]
        F2["Create Pledge<br/>pledge_plg<br/>plg_PledgeOrPayment=Pledge"]
        F3["Set Schedule<br/>plg_schedule"]
    end
    
    subgraph Collection["Collection"]
        C1["Record Payment<br/>pledge_plg<br/>plg_PledgeOrPayment=Payment"]
        C2["Scan Check<br/>fam_scanCheck"]
        C3["Assign Fund<br/>plg_fundID"]
    end
    
    subgraph Deposit["Deposit Process"]
        D1["Create Deposit<br/>deposit_dep"]
        D2["Link Payments<br/>plg_depID"]
        D3["Close Deposit<br/>dep_Closed"]
    end
    
    subgraph Reconciliation["Reconciliation"]
        R1["Bank Reconciliation"]
        R2["Tax Report<br/>plg_NonDeductible"]
        R3["Fund Summary"]
    end
    
    F1 --> F2 --> F3 --> C1 --> C2 --> C3 --> D1 --> D2 --> D3 --> R1 --> R2 --> R3
```

