## 3. Visitor Conversion

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph Visit["Church Visit"]
        V1["First Visit<br/>per_FriendDate"]
        V2["Record Why Came<br/>whycame_why"]
        V3["Add Notes<br/>note_nte"]
    end
    
    subgraph FollowUp["Follow-up Tracking"]
        F1["Assign Property<br/>record2property_r2p"]
        F2["Create Tasks"]
        F3["Send Communications"]
    end
    
    subgraph Classification["Classification"]
        C1["Update Classification<br/>per_cls_ID"]
        C2["Member Status"]
    end
    
    subgraph Integration["Family Integration"]
        I1["Create/Join Family<br/>family_fam"]
        I2["Link to Family<br/>per_fam_ID"]
    end
    
    V1 --> V2 --> V3 --> F1 --> F2 --> F3 --> C1 --> C2
    C2 --> I1 --> I2
```

